<section class="labs-page-title labs-stage40-title"><div><span class="labs-eyebrow">Progress map</span><h1>Track participant progress, receipts, and simulated rewards.</h1><p class="labs-copy">This page turns the Training Lab flow into a usable participant progress map with completion proof and certificate readiness.</p></div><div class="labs-actions"><a class="labs-btn" href="<?php echo labs_url('/app/check-in.php?campaign=' . rawurlencode($campaignRef) . '&user_id=' . $userId); ?>">Check In</a><a class="labs-btn labs-btn-primary" href="<?php echo labs_url('/admin/cohort-manager.php'); ?>">Cohort Manager</a></div></section>
